  "prompt": "Who are some of the famous alumni of NIT Puducherry?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **NIT Puducherry (NITPY)** is a relatively newer institution among the National Institutes of Technology in India, having been established in 2010. Due to its comparatively recent establishment, it may not yet have a large number of widely recognized or \"famous\" alumni in the public domain compared to some of the older NITs like NIT Trichy or NIT Surathkal.\n\nHowever, graduates from NIT Puducherry have been making significant strides in various fields, including:\n\n1. **Engineering and Technology**: Many alumni are employed in leading technology companies, both in India and internationally, working in roles such as software development, data analysis, and systems engineering.\n\n2. **Entrepreneurship**: Some graduates have ventured into startups, contributing to innovative solutions in sectors like fintech, edtech, and sustainable technologies.\n\n3. **Research and Academia**: A number of alumni pursue higher studies, contributing to research in engineering, sciences, and technology both in India and abroad.\n\n4. **Public Sector and Government**: Graduates also take up roles in public sector undertakings and government organizations, contributing to infrastructure, defense, and other critical areas.\n\nWhile specific names of highly prominent individuals may not yet be widely recognized, the alumni network of NIT Puducherry is growing and continuously contributing to various industries and sectors. As the institution matures, it's likely that more of its graduates will gain prominence in their respective fields.\n\nFor the most up-to-date information on notable alumni, you may want to visit the official NIT Puducherry website or their alumni association pages, where achievements and notable careers of alumni are often highlighted.",
